snippet.title: Blood Bar Tycoon 🧛 Early Access Trailer with EN subtitles
snippet.description:
Blood Bar Tycoon is a game where you manage vampire bars! 🧛 

Improve your bars, lure the juiciest humans from the neighborhood, avoid unfortunate incidents, amass wealth and free yourself from your malevolent master!

You like it? Share the video and Wishlist on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2776780/Blood_Bar_Tycoon?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=trailerEA

Made by a group of passionate Belgian game developers!
